#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../pipelight.templates:1001
msgid "Do you want to install Pipelight system-wide?"
msgstr "您想要安裝 Pipelight，並套用到系統全域？"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../pipelight.templates:1001
msgid "There are two ways to install Pipelight:"
msgstr "有兩種方法安裝 Pipelight："

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../pipelight.templates:1001
msgid ""
"When choosing a system-wide installation (default in previous versions) this "
"will allow you and other users on this computer to use Pipelight in every "
"installed browser supporting the NPAPI plugin interface."
msgstr ""
"當選擇系統範圍的安裝( 在之前版本中的預設 )，這將讓您及這台電腦的其他使用者在"
"每個支援 NPAPI 外掛程式介面的已安裝瀏覽器中可以使用 Pipelight 。"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../pipelight.templates:1001
msgid ""
"When not choosing a system-wide installation you will get all files "
"installed, but still have to configure your browser manually to use "
"Pipelight. For instructions on how to do that please visit: https://answers."
"launchpad.net/pipelight/+faq/2362"
msgstr ""
"不選擇系統範圍的安裝，您將獲得安裝的所有檔案，但仍然必須手動設定您的瀏覽器以"
"使用 Pipelight。有關如何做到這一點的說明，請瀏覽：https://answers.launchpad."
"net/pipelight/+faq/2362"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../pipelight.templates:1001
msgid "If unsure choose a systemwide installation."
msgstr "如果不確定，請選擇系統範圍的安裝。"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../pipelight-multi.templates:1001
